    Should Be Equal As Integers  ${server_process.rc}  0
    ${worker_process} =  Run Process  docker pull iexechub/worker:${XTREMWEB_VERSION}-${XTREMWEB_COMMIT_TO_TEST}  shell=yes  stderr=STDOUT  stdout=stdoutxwbuild.txt
